metadata.name: LFG NG-17
metadata.description:
This is the launch of NG-17 from NASA's Wallops Island flight facility in Virginia.  It shows the entire launch trajectory of the rocket as it heads to resupply the International Space Station.  I took an exposure every one second and then stacked them to create this timelapse.  LFG!

Photographer: Jason Betzner

Year Created: 2022

Genre: Photography
